    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >月兔狂想曲企鹅群:123153148</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏默认支持键盘,鼠标操作 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《月兔狂想曲》是一款双主角俯视角动作弹幕射击游戏，你将操作铃仙和妖梦这一攻一受,呸!我是说一攻一守的组合，打败强大的敌人，相较于传统东方弹幕游戏，容错率更高，难度相对低一些。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情简介: </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类的一次登月行动被月兔小队粉碎，得胜的月兔小队乘胜追击，要彻底摧毁人类的火箭发射基地，但不幸被突然出现的人造人击败，只有泠仙一人逃了出来，无法返回月都的她只好逃到幻想乡向永远亭求助，在永琳的命令下，退役多年的月兔老兵再次踏上战场，带着自己的好姬友来到外界拯救被人类俘虏的后辈们，冒险途中她们逐渐接触到人类世界可怕的阴暗面，以及天才美女科学家冈崎梦美的惊天阴谋。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里既有酣畅淋漓的弹幕射击(PS;铃仙残血的时候切换妖梦再切回来可以回血哦，只有简中介绍里告诉你，老外不知道哦，不信你可以切换语言试试)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/e185492b706905e1d4c21346437efa46.poster.avif?t=1761964965\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/e185492b706905e1d4c21346437efa46.webm?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/e185492b706905e1d4c21346437efa46.mp4?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/725da2cb4f194a469f7c12cf1683b3dc.poster.avif?t=1761964965\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/725da2cb4f194a469f7c12cf1683b3dc.webm?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/725da2cb4f194a469f7c12cf1683b3dc.mp4?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也有刀刀到肉的近距离战斗(PS;妖梦不同段的攻击，长按蓄力会有不同的效果哦，我只在中文介绍里告诉你，别告诉老外)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/3fd7ccea40609b7ee623098acc991025.poster.avif?t=1761964965\" width=799 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/3fd7ccea40609b7ee623098acc991025.webm?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至可以弹反</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/bccb68bf818d9fdf57d7ef3fdbc5a5d5.poster.avif?t=1761964965\" width=800 height=451 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230370/extras/bccb68bf818d9fdf57d7ef3fdbc5a5d5.webm?t=1761964965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
